text: Magnus Gällerdal (born 10 August 1979) is a Swedish equestrian. He competed at the 2004 Summer Olympics and the 2008 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Sweden Category:Equestrians at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 2008 Summer Olympics Category:People from Linköping
